  "title": "Not personal",
  "slug": "not-personal",
  "publishedAt": "2021-04-20T05:07:00.000Z",
  "excerpt": "I applied to 3 jobs at 3 companies in same line of work. The same job—relatively—in the same town. 2 offered me a job. 1 didn’t.",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "2 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I applied to 3 jobs at 3 companies in same line of work. The same job—relatively—in the same town. 2 offered me a job. 1 didn’t.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Does that mean there’s a 33% chance I ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "don’t have what it takes",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Or does it simply mean that, while I most certainly have the skills and expertise to do the job, one measly recruiter made a bad call. Based on next to no information. Or some misguided top-down decree.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s not personal.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I reached out to 10 people with the same job in the same industry with the same message. I asked them if they’d mind a short phone call. 4 got back to me. 3 turned me down. 3 ignored my message.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It be foolish to think I need to improve my ‘conversion rate.’ To send a ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "different",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " message to the 6 who didn’t bother.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It could be they’re busy. It could be that they meant to, but forgot. Maybe they don’t check their email, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "who knows?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Whatever the case, there’s a case to be made that there’s absolutely nothing I could have done differently.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s not personal. It’s not a slight ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "on me",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s a completely ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "independent choice",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ". Based on little information. A simple cost/benefit analysis. And a micro-second impression. All in their heads. And, entirely immune to the stories going on outside it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "You see? Rejection is not (always) all about you. Many times, it’s about ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "them",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}